Package: piphub
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash (>= 4.0), git, gh, python3, python3-pip
Recommends: python3-build
Description: GitHub release automation tools
 PipHub provides command-line tools for automating GitHub releases
 and Python package publishing. It includes scripts for both bash
 and PowerShell environments.
 .
 Features:
  - Automated GitHub release creation
  - Python package building and uploading
  - YAML-based configuration
  - Support for draft and prerelease flags
  - Automatic version detection from setup.py
